Who Do You Think You Are? Australia - Series 7, Episode 2




Toni Collette

Actor Toni Collette rose to international fame in her early twenties in the 1994 Australian film Muriel's Wedding. Delving into the enigma of her grandparents she uncovers a tale of abandonment and tragedy, a secret wartime affair, and an unexpected ancestor. And a DNA test serves only to deepen the mystery.




Original Air Date: 11-Aug-2015
